The Presidential Committee on the North-East Initiative (PCNI) has commenced a training workshop on peace-building and transitional justice in Maiduguri, Borno State. The workshop which commenced on Monday the 5th of November is being attended by traditional rulers, judges and religious leaders and is aimed at equipping them with the tools to drive peacebuilding and efforts to entrench access to justice in their communities. Tanimu is an Online Editor with Africa's Largest TV Network. Produces when not on Social media.